{"TopicId":133209,"ForumId":66,"TopicTitle":"Modding Monday: Hangar Grid!","CreatedByName":"SQUAD","CreatedById":66485,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-29T21:01:27Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"SQUAD","CreatedById":66485,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-29T21:01:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cfigure class=\u0022tmblr-full\u0022 data-orig-height=\u002292\u0022 data-orig-width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://36.media.tumblr.com/ab8ca95fa6c767a94ca66db2600759c6/tumblr_inline_o364tvpgK11rr2wit_540.jpg\u0022 data-orig-height=\u002292\u0022 data-orig-width=\u0022480\u0022 alt=\u0022tumblr_inline_o364tvpgK11rr2wit_540.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/figure\u003E\u003Cfigure class=\u0022tmblr-full\u0022 data-orig-height=\u00221080\u0022 data-orig-width=\u00221920\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://41.media.tumblr.com/a4cded05f1bed6085e4646df7ec0517f/tumblr_inline_o364u2tae41rr2wit_540.jpg\u0022 data-orig-height=\u00221080\u0022 data-orig-width=\u00221920\u0022 alt=\u0022tumblr_inline_o364u2tae41rr2wit_540.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/figure\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHave you ever been annoyed by ending up with misaligned engines or clubfooted landing gear after spending half-an-hourtrying just to guess where to rotate to get them right?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://goo.gl/UpytPx\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EThis mod\u003C/a\u003E adds grid to SPH and VAB and \u201Claser\u201D guides for an active part to let you clearly see where the things are wrong! #KSP\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Planetfall","CreatedById":154594,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-29T21:47:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSeems interesting though I don\u0027t think I\u0027d need it that much, but that\u0027s just me.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFirst! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-02-29T21:49:02Z\u0022 title=\u002202/29/2016 09:49  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 29, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Planetfall\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"0111narwhalz","CreatedById":110660,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-29T22:03:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can get the perfect alignment with stock through these steps:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSelect the rotation gizmo\u003Cbr\u003E\nSelect the part\u003Cbr\u003E\nSet to Global mode\u003Cbr\u003E\nSet to Angle Snap\u003Cbr\u003E\nWiggle it around.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDone!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"juanml82","CreatedById":105344,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-29T22:24:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis seems useful when adjusting the mounting points for the ruggerized wheels in my rovers\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Foxster","CreatedById":113764,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-29T22:40:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWorth it just to get landing gear straight.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"BrutalRIP","CreatedById":59065,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-29T23:34:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nits more than just a grid if you watch the \u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HV7pgNqJxfE\u0026amp;feature=youtu.be\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Evid\u003C/a\u003E on the mods OP....very useful when building planes\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-02-29T23:36:03Z\u0022 title=\u002202/29/2016 11:36  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 29, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by BrutalRIP\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Number R09","CreatedById":154153,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-01T01:12:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI \u003Cem\u003Ealmost\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0took up learning to mod because of my desire for such an invention.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nModding Monday\u0027s is now a thing to me. \u00A0Thanks! \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Waxing_Kibbous","CreatedById":151611,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-01T01:48:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s one slick-A unit right there\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ser","CreatedById":104207,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-01T06:11:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222435752\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022133209\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456783414\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110660\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u00220111narwhalz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 hours ago, 0111narwhalz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can get the perfect alignment with stock through these steps:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSelect the rotation gizmo\u003Cbr\u003E\nSelect the part\u003Cbr\u003E\nSet to Global mode\u003Cbr\u003E\nSet to Angle Snap\u003Cbr\u003E\nWiggle it around.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDone!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr you can point at the part and press just one key.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI agree with you, the gizmo in the global mode is a powerful tool. Until you have to align something to an angled wing, for example.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Wallygator","CreatedById":97357,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-01T08:37:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf it will allow me to accurately see the CoM, CoD without stock perspective movement, then I will be very impressed. \u00A0Going to check it out now...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ser","CreatedById":104207,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-01T09:28:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222436407\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022133209\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456821434\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002297357\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Wallygator\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n56 minutes ago, Wallygator said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf it will allow me to accurately see the CoM, CoD without stock perspective movement, then I will be very impressed. \u00A0Going to check it out now...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlready have such suggestion, so check the updates, it\u0027s likely to be there some day.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit: By the way, how would you prefer the CoM, CoL indicators to look like?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-03-01T09:34:48Z\u0022 title=\u002203/01/2016 09:34  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 1, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Ser\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Wallygator","CreatedById":97357,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-01T10:50:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think a bound key to snap the master\u00A0grid to which ever CoX is active at the moment would be helpful. \u00A0Cant\u0027t see a reason to have it for more than one at a time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"0111narwhalz","CreatedById":110660,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-01T16:38:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222436339\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022133209\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456812675\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022104207\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Ser\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, Ser said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUntil you have to align something to an angled wing, for example.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, you could reroot to the wing, and then use absolute.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHowever, this mod is much faster, but I\u0027m not sure if I\u0027d install it due to finite mod space. Of course, that concern goes away as soon as 1.1 occurs (I hope!).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222436427\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022133209\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456824508\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022104207\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Ser\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, Ser said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBy the way, how would you prefer the CoM, CoL indicators to look like?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPersonally, I\u0027d like some alignment indicators to pop out of the axes of the CoX. I mean, I think RCS Build Aid does that, but one mod with both functionalities is better than two with one each.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ser","CreatedById":104207,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-01T17:36:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Ch3\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Ca data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/110660-0111narwhalz/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0026amp;referrer=http%253A%252F%252Fforum.kerbalspaceprogram.com%252Findex.php%253F%252Ftopic%252F133209-modding-monday-hangar-grid%252F\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/110660-0111narwhalz/\u0022 title=\u0022Go to 0111narwhalz\u0027s profile\u0022\u003E0111narwhalz \u003C/a\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis mod is lightweight, it doesn\u0027t use any textures (except for the button, but it is 278 bytes) and all of its objects are removed when you exit the hangar. So you shouldn\u0027t worry about mod space. Anyway, it\u0027s up to you.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Columbia","CreatedById":135031,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-06T02:23:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222435752\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022133209\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456783414\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110660\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u00220111narwhalz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2/29/2016 at 6:03 AM, 0111narwhalz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can get the perfect alignment with stock through these steps:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSelect the rotation gizmo\u003Cbr\u003E\nSelect the part\u003Cbr\u003E\nSet to Global mode\u003Cbr\u003E\nSet to Angle Snap\u003Cbr\u003E\nWiggle it around.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDone!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow do you activate to Global Mode, exactly?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis mod would be useful for aligning landing gear straight.. No more runway-hopping and destruction problems!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"0111narwhalz","CreatedById":110660,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-06T07:03:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222444025\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022133209\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221457230996\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022135031\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Columbia\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, Columbia said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow do you activate to Global Mode, exactly?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis mod would be useful for aligning landing gear straight.. No more runway-hopping and destruction problems!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, you simply hit \u0022F\u0022 (by default).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr, you could install this mod, which (after reading the page and watching the showcase video) has a number of other, very usefull and accessable features.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027d like to apologise to \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/104207-ser/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022104207\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/104207-ser/\u0022\u003E@Ser\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0if I\u0027ve been a bit rude, as well. I\u0027m not trying to discount the effort he\u0027s put into this. Just offering some (contrived, perhaps) stock tricks to replicate some functionality if someone\u0027s phobic of adding mods.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ser","CreatedById":104207,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-06T08:37:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222444225\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022133209\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221457247828\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110660\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u00220111narwhalz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, 0111narwhalz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027d like to apologise to \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/104207-ser/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022104207\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/104207-ser/\u0022\u003E@Ser\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0if I\u0027ve been a bit rude, as well. I\u0027m not trying to discount the effort he\u0027s put into this. Just offering some (contrived, perhaps) stock tricks to replicate some functionality if someone\u0027s phobic of adding mods.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere\u0027s nothing evil in explaining the stock tools usage for people. I\u0027ve switched to the global mode a pair of times accidentally and haven\u0027t realize all the usefulness of it. Should I know about its power I\u0027d had much less pain in vessel design in the past. Also you can see in the video tutorial to my mod that I use it alot now, after its purpose have been explained in the mod\u0027s discussion.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}